 ('1105', 'Acer', 'Acer Liquid Gallant Duo', null, 4.3, 156, 129.0, 65.9, 9.9, '2012-08-21 00:00:00', 'Smart phone', 'Android (4.0.4)', '540 x  960', 256, 'TFT', 5.0, null, 1.0, null, 1500, null, null, '3.0', 'GPS, A-GPS', 'manufacturer/Acer/Acer Liquid Gallant Duo.jpg', 'Acer Liquid Gallant Duo is the dual-SIM brother of the Liquid Gallant, featuring a 1GHz processor made by MediaTek, 1GB of RAM, 4.3-inch screen with qHD resolution (540 by 960 pixels), and 5-megapixel main camera. To no surprise, Android 4.0.4 comes installed out of the box. Last but not least, the smartphone will be available in Gentle Black or Ceramic White.'),
