 ('1120', 'Acer', 'Acer Liquid Z3', null, 3.5, 156, 109.0, 60.0, 10.4, '2013-08-04 00:00:00', 'Smart phone', 'Android (4.2.2)', '320 x  480', 165, 'LCD', 3.0, null, 0.5, 4.0, 1500, null, null, '3.0, EDR', 'GPS, A-GPS', 'manufacturer/Acer/Acer Liquid Z3.jpg', 'The Acer Liquid Z3 is a low-cost model which comes with specs that put it in the entry-level category, including a 1GHz dual-core processor, a 3.5-inch display, 4GB of storage, and a 3MP rear camera. What makes it even clearer that the Acer Liquid Z3 is aimed at budget-conscious buyers is the availability of a dual-SIM version of the device.'),
