 ('1476', 'Alcatel', 'Alcatel Pixi 3 (8) 4G', null, 8.0, null, 209.0, 124.9, 8.3, '2016-01-04 00:00:00', 'Tablet', 'Windows (10 Mobile)', '800 x  1280', 189, 'IPS LCD', 5.0, 2.0, 1.0, null, 4060, null, null, '4.1', 'GPS, A-GPS', 'manufacturer/Alcatel/Alcatel Pixi 3 (8) 4G.jpg', 'The Alcatel Pixi 3 (8) 4G features 8-inch display with resolution of 800 x 1280 pixels. The tablet is powered by Qualcomm Snapdragon 210 SOC, accompanied with 1GB of RAM and 8 gigs of memory. A microSD slot is available for memory expansion. There is 5 megapixel camera on the back, as well as 2 megapixel front one. A 4060mAh battery keeps the lights on.'),
