 ('1504', 'Amazon', 'Amazon Kindle Fire HD', 199, 7.0, 482, 193.0, 137.0, 10.3, '2012-09-06 00:00:00', 'Tablet', 'Android (4.0)', '1280 x  800', 216, 'IPS LCD', null, 1.3, 1.0, 16.0, null, null, null, 'Yes', 'Wi-Fi positioning', 'manufacturer/Amazon/Amazon Kindle Fire HD.jpg', 'The new Amazon Kindle Fire HD 7-inch is a tablet with an impressive resolution of 1200 x 800 pixels and an IPS LCD screen. It packs a 1.2GHz processor that Amazon brags outperforms the Tegra 3. The price is set at the low $199.'),
