 ('1633', 'Asus', 'Asus MeMO Pad HD 7', 129, 7.0, 482, 196.8, 120.6, 10.8, null, 'Tablet', 'Android (4.2.1)', '1280 x  800', 216, 'IPS LCD', 5.0, 1.2, 1.0, 8.0, null, null, null, 'Yes', 'GPS', 'manufacturer/Asus/Asus MeMO Pad HD 7.jpg', 'The Asus MeMO Pad HD 7 comes with a 1280 by 800 pixel IPS display, a quad-core processor and 1GB of RAM. In addition, there''s a 1.2MP front-facing cam for video chats on the Asus MeMO Pad HD 7. In case one demands having a more decent snapper as well, a 5MP rear camera for photos and videos comes as an option. Software-wise, we have Android 4.2 Jelly Bean running on the MeMO Pad HD 7.'),
 ('1634', 'Asus', 'Asus MeMO Pad Smart 10', 299, 10.1, 482, 263.0, 180.8, 9.9, '2013-02-08 00:00:00', 'Tablet', 'Android (4.1)', '1280 x  800', 149, 'IPS LCD', 5.0, 1.2, 1.0, 16.0, null, null, null, '3.0, EDR', 'GPS', 'manufacturer/Asus/Asus MeMO Pad Smart 10.jpg', 'The Asus MeMO Pad Smart 10 is an Android 4.1-based tablet. It offers a 10.1'''' IPS display with 1280 x 800 px resolution, NVIDIA Tegra 3 quad-core processor, 1 gig of RAM, 4 GB memory and a microSD card slot.'),
