 ('2049', 'Celkon', 'Celkon A107+', null, 5.0, null, null, null, null, null, 'Smart phone', 'Android (4.2.2)', '480 x  800', 187, null, 8.0, 1.3, 0.5, null, 2100, null, null, 'Yes', 'GPS, A-GPS', 'manufacturer/Celkon/Celkon A107+.jpg', 'The Celkon A107+ is a mid-range phone with Android 4.2.2, dual SIM card support, 5" display with 480 x 800 px resolution, 1 GHz dual core CPU, 512 MB RAM, microSD slot and 2 cams - 8 MP rear snapper and a 1.3 MP front one.'),
 ('2050', 'Celkon', 'Celkon A107', null, 5.0, null, 148.0, 77.2, 9.6, null, 'Smart phone', 'Android (4.0.2)', '480 x  800', 187, 'TFT', 8.0, 0.3, 0.5, null, 2100, 7.0, 300.0, 'Yes', 'GPS, A-GPS', 'manufacturer/Celkon/Celkon A107.jpg', 'The Celkon A107 is a smartphone running Android 4.0.2. It comes equipped with a 5" display, 1 GHz dual core processor, 512 MB RAM and 512 MB ROM, microSD slot and two cameras - 8MP main and 0.3 MP secondary cams.'),
 ('2051', 'Celkon', 'Celkon A115', null, 5.0, 156, 148.0, 74.0, 9.3, null, 'Smart phone', 'Android (4.2.2)', '480 x  854', 196, 'IPS LCD', 8.0, 1.3, 0.5, 4.0, 2000, null, null, 'Yes', 'GPS, A-GPS', 'manufacturer/Celkon/Celkon A115.jpg', 'The Celkon A115 is a dual SIM Android 4.2.2 phone. With a 5" display, it is powered by a dual core processor, clocked at 1.3 GHz, coupled with 512 MB RAM, and 4 GB storage space, plus microSD slot. On the back there is an 8 MP camera, and on the front - 1.3 MP one.'),
