 ('2054', 'Celkon', 'Celkon A125', null, 4.5, 156, 138.0, 68.5, 10.0, null, 'Smart phone', 'Android (4.2.2)', '854 x  960', 286, 'TFT', 5.0, 1.3, 0.5, 4.0, 2000, null, null, 'Yes', 'GPS, A-GPS', 'manufacturer/Celkon/Celkon A125.jpg', 'The Celkon A125 is a mid-range Android 4.2.2-flaunting device. It comes with a 4.5" display, 5 MP main camera, 1.3 MP front-facing cam, 512 MB RAM, 4 GB storage and a 1.3 GHz dual core CPU. It also offers dual SIM card support .'),
 ('2055', 'Celkon', 'Celkon A15', null, 3.5, null, null, null, null, null, 'Smart phone', 'Android (4.2.2)', '320 x  480', 165, null, 3.2, null, 0.25, null, 1400, null, null, 'Yes', 'GPS, A-GPS', 'manufacturer/Celkon/Celkon A15.jpg', 'The Celkon A15 is a low-end Android 4.2.2 smartphone. Its specifications are pretty basic - 3.5" display, 1 GHz dual core CPU, 256 MB RAM / 512 MB ROM, microSD card slot, as well as a 3.2 MP camera. The phone supports two SIM cards.'),
 ('2056', 'Celkon', 'Celkon A1', null, 3.2, 156, 113.5, 54.5, 12.3, null, 'Smart phone', 'Android (2.2)', '240 x  400', 146, null, 2.0, null, null, null, 1000, 5.0, 400.0, 'Yes', 'GPS, A-GPS', 'manufacturer/Celkon/Celkon A1.jpg', 'The Celkon A1 is an Android smartphone with 2 SIM card slots. It comes with Android 2.2, 3.2" Display, 2MP Camera, Bluetooth, multimedia players, FM Radio, 32GB Expandable Memory and the usual features of the OS.'),
 ('2057', 'Celkon', 'Celkon A20', null, 4.0, null, null, null, null, null, 'Smart phone', 'Android (4.2)', '480 x  800', 233, 'TFT', 3.2, 0.3, 0.25, null, 1500, null, null, 'Yes', 'GPS, A-GPS', 'manufacturer/Celkon/Celkon A20.jpg', 'The Celkon A20 is a powerful Android phone with version 4.2 of the platform, 4" display, 1.2 GHz dual core CPU, 256 MB RAM / 512 MB ROM, microSD card slot for up to 32 GB additional memory, and 2 cameras - 3.2 MP main one and a VGA front shooter.'),
 ('2058', 'Celkon', 'Celkon A21', null, 4.0, 156, 124.8, 66.1, 10.8, null, 'Smart phone', 'Android (4.2.2)', '320 x  480', 144, null, 3.2, 1.3, 0.25, 0.512, 1500, null, null, '4.0', 'GPS, A-GPS', 'manufacturer/Celkon/Celkon A21.jpg', 'The Celkon A21 is low-end Android 4.2.2-flaunting phone. Specs-wise it is a bit modest - it offers a 4" 320 x 480 px display, 1.2 GHz dual core processor, coupled with 256 MB RAM, 512 MB native storage and a microSD card slot for added capacity. The camera on the back is a 3.2 MP one, and on the front the Celkon A21 is equipped with a 1.3 MP selfie shooter.'),
 ('2059', 'Celkon', 'Celkon A333', null, 3.5, 156, null, null, null, null, 'Smart phone', 'Android (4.4.2)', '320 x  480', 165, 'LCD', 2.0, 1.3, 0.25, 0.512, 1100, null, null, 'Yes', 'GPS, A-GPS', 'manufacturer/Celkon/Celkon A333.jpg', 'The Celkon A333 is a basic smartphone with Android 4.4.2. Its specs are nothing to write home about - 3.5" 320 x 480 px display, 1 GHz processor, and 2 MP rear camera, along with 1.3 MP front one. Dual SIM card support is on board as well.'),
