 ('2424', 'Gionee', 'Gionee Marathon M5', 370, 5.5, 156, 152.0, 76.0, 8.5, '2015-06-10 00:00:00', 'Smart phone', 'Android (5.1)', '720 x  1280', 267, 'AMOLED', 13.0, 5.0, 2.0, 16.0, 6020, null, null, '4.0', 'GPS, A-GPS', 'manufacturer/Gionee/Gionee Marathon M5.jpg', 'Gionee''s Marathon M5 smartphone features a monster battery - in fact, it''s two 3010 mAh juice packs. It includes a number of battery optimization features to ensure that it can outrun most other smartphones on the market. Whilst the Marathon M5''s name gives it away as a long-distance runner as opposed to a sprint specialist, its specs are still reasonably solid. It bundles a quad-core 1.3 GHz processor, 2 GB of RAM, a 13-megapixel rear shooter, 4G LTE and 16GB of on-board storage, which can be expanded by means of the microSD slot. The 5.5-inch AMOLED display is only a 720 x 1280 offering.'),
