 ('2594', 'HTC', 'HTC MAX 4G', null, 3.8, 156, 113.5, 63.1, 13.9, '2008-11-13 00:00:00', 'Smart phone', 'Windows Mobile Professional (6.1)', '480 x  800', 246, 'TFT', 3.2, null, 0.3, 8.0, 1500, 7.0, 350.0, '2.0, EDR', 'GPS', 'manufacturer/HTC/HTC MAX 4G.jpg', 'HTC MAX 4G is the first GSM/WiMAX phone to come to the market. WiMAX is a 4G network, for high-speed internet access. The MAX 4G is similar to the Touch HD in its specs, with 3.8" WVGA display and 3.2-megapixel camera. It is announced for the Russian market only.'),
