 ('2925', 'Huawei', 'Huawei Vision', null, 3.7, 156, 118.5, 59.5, 9.9, null, 'Smart phone', 'Android (2.3)', '800 x  480', 252, null, 5.0, 0.3, 0.5, null, 1400, 6.6, 400.0, '2.1', 'GPS', 'manufacturer/Huawei/Huawei Vision.jpg', 'The Huawei Vision is a stylish smartphone in a unibody frame. It comes with Android Gingerbread and features a curved 3.7" display, a 1GHz processor and 5MP camera. It also features the standard set of connectivity options - Wi-Fi, Bluetooth, and has a microSD card slot supporting up to 32GB additional memory.'),
