 ('3652', 'LG', 'LG GB115', null, 1.5, 156, 103.5, 45.0, 14.5, null, null, null, '128 x  128', 121, 'CSTN', 0.3, null, null, null, 950, 4.0, 100.0, null, null, 'manufacturer/LG/LG GB115.jpg', 'LG GB115 is a simple dual-band GSM phone. It features 65k color TFT display, VGA camera, FM Radio, MP3 player and microSD slot for memory.'),
 ('3653', 'LG', 'LG GB125R', null, 1.5, 156, 87.0, 45.0, 19.3, null, 'Basic phone', null, '128 x  128', 121, 'CSTN', null, null, null, null, 950, 6.5, 440.0, null, null, 'manufacturer/LG/LG GB125R.jpg', 'The LG GB125R is a low-end clamshell that lacks an external display, replacing it with a series of status indication lights. It has a FM Radio, 65K color display and speakerphone.'),
