 ('3712', 'LG', 'LG Glance', null, 2.0, 156, 109.0, 47.0, 10.0, '2009-05-28 00:00:00', null, null, '240 x  320', 200, 'TFT', 1.3, null, null, null, 800, 4.33, 350.0, '2.1, EDR', 'GPS', 'manufacturer/LG/LG Glance.jpg', 'The LG Glance is a basic candybar, targeting users who seek for a more affordable phone. However it does have a little something to make it distinguishable and that is the golden-like pattern on the back, which, combined with the really thin body, measuring at only 0.38 inches, gives it a really fashionable look. Specs wise, the Glance offers a 2-inch QVGA screen and 1.3-megapixel camera'),
 ('3713', 'LG', 'LG Glimmer', null, 2.8, 156, 101.6, 52.0, 15.0, '2008-03-11 00:00:00', null, null, '240 x  400', 167, 'TFT', 2.0, null, null, 0.128, 800, 3.5, 168.0, '1.2', 'GPS', 'manufacturer/LG/LG Glimmer.jpg', 'LG Glimmer is a Shine-like slider in design, but replaces the display and navigation keys with larger 2.8" 240x400-pixels touchscreen. It slides open to reveal standard numeric keypad, for dialing a number or text input. Glimmer is CDMA/EV-DO phone with 2-megapixel camera, microSD and Stereo Bluetooth.'),
