 ('3716', 'LG', 'LG Harmony', null, 5.3, 156, 149.9, 76.2, 7.6, null, 'Smart phone', 'Android (7.0), LG UX UI', '720 x  1280', 277, 'TFT', 8.0, 5.0, 1.5, 16.0, 2800, 14.0, 350.0, '4.2', 'GPS, A-GPS', 'manufacturer/LG/LG Harmony.jpg', 'The LG Harmony has a fairly big 5.3-inch display with a 720p resolution that''s not as sharp as 1080p, but still quite serviceable. There are an 8MP rear camera, a 5MP selfie snapper, and 16GB of expandable storage. Also – wait for it – a fingerprint scanner! Yes, there''s one on the back of the phone.'),
 ('3717', 'LG', 'LG INCITE', null, 3.0, 156, 107.0, 56.0, 14.0, null, 'Smart phone', 'Windows Mobile Professional (6.1)', '240 x  400', 155, 'TFT', 3.0, null, 0.1, 0.07, 1300, 8.7, 504.0, '2.0, EDR', 'GPS', 'manufacturer/LG/LG INCITE.jpg', 'LG INCITE is a global GSM/3G phone with Wi-Fi, GPS for AT&T Navigator and 3 MP camera. It has WQVGA 240x400 pixels display and is running Windows Mobile 6.1 Professional with personalized interface (with a menu resembling the Vu’s one).'),
 ('3718', 'LG', 'LG IQ GW825', null, 3.2, 156, 113.0, 55.0, 15.9, null, 'Smart phone', 'Windows Mobile Professional (6.5)', '480 x  800', 292, 'TFT', 5.0, null, 0.25, null, null, 6.0, 400.0, '2.1, EDR', 'A-GPS', 'manufacturer/LG/LG IQ GW825.jpg', 'The LG IQ GW825 is a business-oriented smartphone, running the Windows Mobile 6.5 operating system. It packs a fingerprint sensor, a 3.2-inch screen and a slide-out QWERTY keyboard.'),
 ('3719', 'LG', 'LG Intuition', null, 5.0, 156, 139.6, 90.4, 8.5, '2012-09-04 00:00:00', 'Smart phone', 'Android (4.0.4), Optimus UI', '768 x  1024', 256, 'IPS LCD', 8.0, 1.3, 1.0, 32.0, 2080, 16.07, 130.0, '3.0', 'GPS', 'manufacturer/LG/LG Intuition.jpg', 'This is Verizon''s version of the LG Optimus Vu and it will be released with Ice Cream Sandwich out of the box, not the aging Android 2.3 Gingerbread like on the original. Other than that LG Intuition offers a dual-core 1.5GHz processor, 1GB of RAM, 32GB of storage, an 8-megapixel camera, and, of course, a gigantic, 5-inch display with resolution of 1024 by 768 pixels and 4:3 aspect ratio.'),
