 ('3721', 'LG', 'LG Jil Sander Mobile', null, 3.8, 156, 123.0, 61.5, 11.5, '2010-10-11 00:00:00', 'Smart phone', 'Windows Phone, 7.5 Mango', '480 x  800', 246, 'TFT', 5.0, null, null, 16.0, 1500, 7.0, 400.0, '2.1, EDR', 'A-GPS', 'manufacturer/LG/LG Jil Sander Mobile.jpg', 'Jil Sander Mobile is a Windows Phone 7.5 Mango device designed by the fashion designer Jil Sander and is manufactured by LG. In terms of hardware specs, this is nothing we haven’t seen before, since it features a 3.8” WVGA display, 5-megapixel auto-focus camera with flash, 1GHz single-core processor, 720p video recording, and Windows Phone 7.5 Mango.'),
