 ('3890', 'LG', 'LG Optimus Black', null, 4.0, 156, 122.0, 64.0, 9.2, '2011-01-05 00:00:00', 'Smart phone', 'Android (2.3, 2.2)', '480 x  800', 233, 'IPS LCD', 5.0, 2.0, 0.5, 1.0, 1500, 6.0, 350.0, 'Yes', 'A-GPS', 'manufacturer/LG/LG Optimus Black.jpg', 'The LG Optimus Black (also known as the LG B) has the specs to be called the "thinnest and brighest" smartphone measuring 9.2mm and offering a 4 inch NOVA display which is said to offer 700 nits of brightness. The device is running Android 2.2 with Optimus UI 2.0 on top of it.'),
