 ('4070', 'LG', 'LG VX9400', null, 2.2, 156, 102.0, 49.0, 18.5, null, null, null, '320 x  240', 182, 'TFT', 1.3, null, null, null, 950, 3.8, 458.0, '1.2', 'GPS', 'manufacturer/LG/LG VX9400.jpg', 'LG VX9400 is TV-capable phone using Verizon''s MediaFlo VCAST TV technology. It has swiveling QVGA display that is 2.2 inches large. The 9400 features 1.3-megapixel camera with flash, stereo Bluetooth, and has microSD slot for memory expansion'),
