 ('4181', 'Lenovo', 'Lenovo IdeaTab A1000', null, 7.0, 482, 199.0, 121.0, 10.7, '2013-02-24 00:00:00', 'Tablet', 'Android (4.1)', '1024 x  600', 170, 'TFT', null, 0.3, 1.0, 16.0, 3500, null, null, '3.0', 'GPS', 'manufacturer/Lenovo/Lenovo IdeaTab A1000.jpg', 'The 7" Lenovo A1000 is an entry level warrior, powered by a 1.2GHz dual-core MTK processor, chewing through the Jelly Bean interface with sufficient decency. \nIt is a fairly thick slab with quite the bezel surrounding the 7" 1024x600 pixels display, which is not IPS, hence with weak viewing angles. The A1000 has a microSD slot in addition to the 16 GB of internal storage, and two front speakers with surround sound technology.'),
