 ('5273', 'Nokia', 'Nokia 5800 Navigation Edition', null, 3.2, 156, 111.0, 51.7, 15.5, '2009-08-21 00:00:00', 'Smart phone', 'Symbian (9.4), S60 5th Edition', '360 x  640', 229, 'TFT', 3.2, null, 0.1, null, 1320, 8.8, 406.0, '2.0, EDR', 'A-GPS', 'manufacturer/Nokia/Nokia 5800 Navigation Edition.jpg', 'The Nokia 5800 Navigation Edition is the same as the 5800 XpressMusic, but comes with a life-long license for both walk and drive navigation and the box contains a car charger and kit. The 5800 Navigation Edition also runs the Symbian S60 5th Edition OS and is a mid-level phone featuring a 3.2-inch 360x640 pixels display, 3.2MP camera, Wi-Fi, GPS, and 3.5mm jack.'),
