 ('5411', 'Nokia', 'Nokia 7610 / 7610B', null, 0.0, 156, 108.6, 53.0, 18.7, '2004-03-18 00:00:00', 'Smart phone', 'Symbian (7.0s), S60 2nd Edition, Feature Pack 1', '176 x  208', null, 'TFT', 1.0, null, null, 0.008, 900, 3.0, 250.0, '1.2', null, 'manufacturer/Nokia/Nokia 7610 _ 7610B.jpg', 'Nokia 7610 is sleek and compact global roaming GSM phone. It sports 65k color display, built-in 1M pixel camera, GPRS data, speakerphone, RS-MMC card slot, polyphonic ringing tones, Java MIDP 2.0, Internet browser and voice functions. It runs Series 60 over Symbian OS 7.0s.'),
