 ('5431', 'Nokia', 'Nokia 8', 599, 5.3, 156, 151.5, 73.7, 7.9, '2017-08-16 00:00:00', 'Smart phone', 'Android (7.1)', '1440 x  2560', 554, 'IPS LCD', 13.0, 13.0, 4.0, 64.0, 3090, null, null, '5.0', 'GPS, A-GPS, Glonass, BeiDou', 'manufacturer/Nokia/Nokia 8.jpg', 'The Nokia 8 comes with Qualcomm''s Snapdragon 835, 4GB RAM and 64GB internal memory. The screen measures 5.3-inches with 1440x2560 pixels resolution. For the purpose of taking pictures, the Nokia 8 comes with 3 cameras all of them 13-megapixels. Two on the back (one of which shoots monochrome images) and one on the front. The Gloss Blue color has beefier 128GB of storage.'),
 ('5432', 'Nokia', 'Nokia 9290', null, 0.0, 156, 158.0, 56.0, 27.0, '2001-06-05 00:00:00', 'Smart phone', 'Symbian (6.0)', '640 x  200', null, 'TFT', null, null, null, null, 1300, 10.0, 220.0, null, null, 'manufacturer/Nokia/Nokia 9290.jpg', 'The Nokia 9290 runs Symbian OS, has email and JAVA support, expandable MMC memory slot, large TFT color display, HTML and E-mail support.'),
 ('5433', 'Nokia', 'Nokia 9300', null, 0.0, 156, 132.0, 51.0, 21.0, '2004-09-08 00:00:00', 'Smart phone', 'Symbian (7.0s), Series 80 2nd Edition', '640 x  200', null, 'TFT', null, null, null, 0.08, 970, 4.0, 200.0, '1.1', null, 'manufacturer/Nokia/Nokia 9300.jpg', 'Nokia 9300 is the second device from the company using Series 80 interface. The business oriented phone supports large TFT display, EDGE/GRPS data, Bluetooth, Infrared port, MMC card slot, Java MIDP 2.0, HTML browser, music player and full QWERTY keyboard.'),
 ('5434', 'Nokia', 'Nokia 9300i', null, 0.0, 156, 132.0, 51.0, 21.0, '2005-11-29 00:00:00', 'Smart phone', 'Symbian (7.0s), Series 80 2nd Edition', '640 x  200', null, 'TFT', null, null, null, 0.08, 1100, 8.0, 230.0, '1.2', null, 'manufacturer/Nokia/Nokia 9300i.jpg', 'Nokia 9300i is the successor of the 9300 and shares most of it features and specifications. It improves the battery times and adds WLAN connectivity. The 9300i has full QWERTY keyboard and support for EMAIL, IM, and HTML browsing'),
 ('5435', 'Nokia', 'Nokia 9500 Communicator', null, 0.0, 156, 148.0, 57.0, 24.0, '2004-02-23 00:00:00', 'Smart phone', 'Symbian (7.0s), Series 80 2nd Edition', '640 x  200', null, 'TFT', 0.3, null, null, 0.08, 1300, 6.0, 300.0, '1.1', null, 'manufacturer/Nokia/Nokia 9500 Communicator.jpg', 'Nokia 9500 the latest edition to the Communicator series. It features global roaming, Bluetooth, Java, WI-Fi, dual displays, MMS and web-browsing.'),
