 ('5592', 'Nokia', 'Nokia X6 16GB Latin America', null, 3.2, 156, 111.0, 51.0, 13.8, '2010-01-26 00:00:00', 'Smart phone', 'Symbian (9.4), S60 5th Edition', '360 x  640', 229, 'TFT', 5.0, null, 0.1, 16.0, 1320, 11.5, 420.0, '2.0, EDR', 'GPS', 'manufacturer/Nokia/Nokia X6 16GB Latin America.jpg', 'Nokia X6 is the most technologically advanced music-oriented handset of the manufacturer to date and sports 3.2-inch touch sensitive screen, 16GB built-in memory, 5-megapixel camera with double LED flash and Carl Zeiss optics, A-GPS, 3.5mm jack and battery that will allow 35hrs of continuous audio playback.'),
