 ('5974', 'Samsung', 'Samsung ATIV Tab 7', null, 11.6, 482, 304.0, 189.4, 11.89, '2012-08-29 00:00:00', 'Tablet', 'Windows (8)', '1920 x  1080', 190, 'LCD', 5.0, 2.0, null, 256.0, null, null, null, '4.0', null, 'manufacturer/Samsung/Samsung ATIV Tab 7.jpg', 'The Samsung ATIV Tab 7 (previously known as ATIV Smart PC Pro) is a productivity machine with Intel’s Core-i5 chip powering Windows 8 on an 11.6-inch display, which docks into a keyboard base. It gets 8.5 hours of battery life and comes with Samsung’s S Pen slotted inside.'),
