 ('6137', 'Samsung', 'Samsung Exhibit 4G', null, 3.5, 156, 119.0, 58.0, 13.0, '2011-06-01 00:00:00', 'Smart phone', 'Android (2.3)', '480 x  800', 267, 'TFT', 3.0, 0.3, 0.5, null, 1500, 6.5, 350.0, '3.0', 'GPS', 'manufacturer/Samsung/Samsung Exhibit 4G.jpg', 'The Samsung Exhibit 4G comes to market with Android 2.3 installed and a 1GHz Hummingbird processor under the hood. It has 3.5" TFT display with resolution of 480x800 pixels. The handset features s VGA front-facing camera while the shooter on back is 3MP. Of course, the phone wouldn''t be the Samsung Exhibit 4G without 4G connectivity which is accomplished through T-Mobile''s HSPA+ network.'),
