 ('6145', 'Samsung', 'Samsung Flight', null, 0.0, 156, 106.0, 56.0, 13.0, '2009-10-05 00:00:00', null, null, '240 x  320', null, 'TFT', 2.0, null, null, 0.08, 1000, 3.0, 360.0, '2.0, EDR', 'GPS', 'manufacturer/Samsung/Samsung Flight.jpg', 'The Samsung Flight is a messaging-centric phone that sports both a touchscreen and a vertical-sliding QWERTY keyboard. It also has a 2-megapixel camera, Stereo Bluetooth, microSD card slot and 3G support for fast access to the web.'),
 ('6146', 'Samsung', 'Samsung FlipShot', null, 0.0, 156, 95.5, 46.5, 18.5, '2007-11-21 00:00:00', null, null, '240 x  320', null, 'TFT', 3.0, null, null, null, 880, 4.0, 350.0, '1.2', 'GPS', 'manufacturer/Samsung/Samsung FlipShot.jpg', 'Samsung U900 is the successor of the A990 - dedicated cameraphone with 3-megapixel autofocus camera and swiveling QVGA display. It also improves on the video capture resolution in order to work also as a camcorder.'),
 ('6147', 'Samsung', 'Samsung Focus 2', null, 4.0, 156, 122.0, 63.0, 11.0, '2012-05-07 00:00:00', 'Smart phone', 'Windows Phone, 7.5 Mango', '480 x  800', 233, 'Super AMOLED', 5.0, 0.3, null, 8.0, 1750, 6.0, 250.0, '2.1, EDR', 'A-GPS', 'manufacturer/Samsung/Samsung Focus 2.jpg', 'Samsung Focus 2 is AT&T''s third 4G LTE offering running the Windows Phone OS. The Focus 2 is following the Focus, Focus Flash and Focus S and comes with a 4-inch Super AMOLED screen and 5-megapixel camera that makes taking pictures or shooting video in HD 720p a breeze. The front-facing VGA camera provides the ability for video chat.'),
 ('6148', 'Samsung', 'Samsung Focus Flash', 400, 3.7, 156, 116.0, 59.0, 11.0, '2011-09-12 00:00:00', 'Smart phone', 'Windows Phone, 7.5 Mango', '480 x  800', 252, 'Super AMOLED', 5.0, null, 0.5, 8.0, 1500, 6.5, 250.0, '2.1, EDR', 'GPS', 'manufacturer/Samsung/Samsung Focus Flash.jpg', 'Samsung Focus Flash is a Windows Phone 7.5 Mango running device with 3.7-inch Super AMOLED screen. It is powered by a 1.4 GHz processor and features a 5-megapixel camera plus front facing one.'),
 ('6149', 'Samsung', 'Samsung Focus S', 550, 4.3, 156, 126.0, 67.0, 8.0, '2011-09-12 00:00:00', 'Smart phone', 'Windows Phone, 7.5 Mango', '480 x  800', 217, 'Super AMOLED Plus', 8.0, 1.3, null, 16.0, 1650, 6.5, 250.0, '2.1, EDR', 'GPS', 'manufacturer/Samsung/Samsung Focus S.jpg', 'The Samsung Focus S strips much of the bulk of the original Focus as it comes with a thin 0.34-inch (8.55mm) body. Under the hood, a 1.4GHz processor runs the Mango goodness. An 8-megapixel camera on the back will add appeal to the Focus S, while up front it comes with a 1.3-megapixel snapper for video conferencing.'),
