 ('6494', 'Samsung', 'Samsung M3310', null, 2.1, 156, 101.0, 47.8, 15.9, null, null, null, '240 x  320', 190, 'TFT', 3.2, null, null, 0.04, 960, 4.8, 330.0, '2.1, EDR', null, 'manufacturer/Samsung/Samsung M3310.jpg', 'Samsung M3310 is a music-oriented handset coming in a dual-slider form factor (like the Samsung F400). The M3310 is equipped with a decent set of functions and features like 2.1-inc QVGA display, 3.2-megapixel camera, 3.5mm jack, FM radio with RDS, microSD card slot and Bluetooth.'),
 ('6495', 'Samsung', 'Samsung M360', 210, 0.0, 156, 99.0, 48.0, 18.0, null, 'Basic phone', null, '240 x  320', null, null, 1.3, null, 128.0, null, 1000, 6.2, 254.0, '2.1, EDR', 'E911', 'manufacturer/Samsung/Samsung M360.jpg', 'Samsung M360 is a basic clamshell phone for those who want a phone that just does the basics. It comes equipped with a 1.3MP camera, SMS and speakerphone.'),
