 ('7305', 'Sony', 'Sony Ericsson K630', null, 0.0, 156, 103.0, 47.0, 15.5, '2007-10-11 00:00:00', null, null, '176 x  220', null, 'TFT', 2.0, null, null, 0.032, 950, 9.0, 300.0, '2.0', null, 'manufacturer/Sony/Sony Ericsson K630.jpg', 'The Sony Ericsson K630 is a quad-band GSM with single-band UMTS/HSDPA support, in a candybar design. It features 2-megapixel camera with dedicated key, M2 slot for memory, multimedia player and FM Radio.'),
