 ('7314', 'Sony', 'Sony Ericsson Live with Walkman', null, 3.2, 156, 106.0, 56.5, 14.2, '2011-08-22 00:00:00', 'Smart phone', 'Android (4.0, 2.3)', '320 x  480', 180, 'TFT', 5.0, null, 0.5, 0.32, 1200, 14.25, 400.0, 'Yes', 'A-GPS, Glonass', 'manufacturer/Sony/Sony Ericsson Live with Walkman.jpg', 'Sony Ericsson Live with Walkman is the second Walkman branded Android phone from the manufacturer. It features a 3.2" touch screen, 5MP camera with HD recording capabilities, Wi-Fi, GPS and microSDHC card slot. It is said to bring a "Deep Facebook integration" which allows users to instantly access Facebook through the most used areas of the phone such as the picture gallery, music player, phonebook and calendar.'),
