 ('7452', 'Sony', 'Sony Ericsson Zylo', null, 2.6, 156, 103.0, 52.0, 16.0, '2010-04-13 00:00:00', 'Feature phone', null, '240 x  320', 154, 'TFT', 3.2, null, null, 0.26, 920, 4.0, 339.0, '2.1, EDR', null, 'manufacturer/Sony/Sony Ericsson Zylo.jpg', 'Sony Ericsson Zylo is a GSM slider phone targeted to the music lovers. It plays FLAC music files and is equipped with microSDHC card slot for plenty of storage. It also features FM radio, stereo Bluetooth and 3.2MP camera.'),
