 ('7542', 'Spice', 'Spice Mobile Coolpad 2', null, 4.5, null, null, null, null, null, 'Smart phone', 'Android (4.1)', '540 x  960', 245, 'TFT', 5.0, null, 1.0, 4.0, 1700, null, null, 'Yes', 'GPS, A-GPS', 'manufacturer/Spice/Spice Mobile Coolpad 2.jpg', 'The Spice Mobile Coolpad 2 is a smartphone with Android 4.1. Its specs include 4.5" display, 1.2 GHz quad core CPU, 1 GB RAM, 4 GB ROM, microSD slot, and a 5 MP camera on the back.'),
