 ('7684', 'T-Mobile', 'T-Mobile Sparq II', null, 2.4, 156, 118.0, 54.0, 15.0, null, 'Basic phone', null, '240 x  320', 167, null, 2.0, null, 0.1, null, null, 5.5, 420.0, 'Yes', null, 'manufacturer/T-Mobile/T-Mobile Sparq II.jpg', 'The T-Mobile Sparq II is a basic phone that features a 2.4'''' display and a side-sliding QWERTY keyboard. It also offers FM radio, 2MP camera, 128 MB RAM / 256 MB ROM and microSD card slot.'),
