 ('7686', 'T-Mobile', 'T-Mobile SpringBoard', null, 7.0, 482, 190.0, 129.0, 10.0, '2011-10-09 00:00:00', 'Tablet', 'Android (4.0.4, 3.2)', '1280 x  800', 216, 'TFT', 5.0, 1.3, 1.0, 16.0, 4100, null, null, '2.1, EDR', 'GPS, A-GPS', 'manufacturer/T-Mobile/T-Mobile SpringBoard.jpg', 'The T-Mobile SpringBoard is an Android 3.2 tablet with a 7-inch touchscreen display, 1.2 GHz dual core processor, 5-megapixel camera, 16GB of internal memory and a second 1.3-megapixel shooter.'),
